=== Ruby CSS Library

Use Cascading Style Sheets in Ruby.

==== Setup

Install the gem with RubyGems.

   gem install tfcss

==== An example

  require 'css'
  include Css

  stylesheet = Stylesheet.new 'My Shiny Style', <<STR
  body {
    margin: 0;
  }
  a img {
    border: none;
  }
  STR

  stylesheet.elements


==== Testing

You can run the suite of unit tests using <tt>rake test</tt>.


